name: Run Through The Window!
description:
This is a piece I made when I felt burnout lately. Took me days to finish this one. It seemed like someone stole my sweet ideas and left me with nothing. But God is good as I found an inspiration through @jjjjjjjjjjohn's artwork. So here's my tribute to his magnificent "window" creation.

The lemon thieves in this artwork represent the thieves who stole my ideas, so don't let them escape this time!
